28:53.020 --> 28:54.620
It's using RDP.

28:54.620 --> 28:56.380
And the XRDP project has actually

28:56.380 --> 28:58.180
gotten some love in the last few years.

28:58.180 --> 29:00.640
So it's stayed pretty performant.

29:00.640 --> 29:06.060
