OK, honestly, the first time I just

30:23.140 --> 30:24.820
used Netcat to get some data in there,

30:24.820 --> 30:27.260
that was before I discovered the handy clipboard support.

30:27.260 --> 30:28.020
Amazing.

30:28.020 --> 30:28.500
Amazing.

